{"tid":779840,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★沈振盈：貴就要跌　話之你係藍籌","createTime":"2018-08-14T16:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T22:47:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8681669bf7953f2cc6d4ff4870a68184f0c729","tid":779840,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:39:09.000Z","msg":"訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈在東方產經「大師教路」專欄表示，上周原本出現的反彈浪，遇上突發的土耳其危機，導致這兩天港股被打了下來，恒指又折返起步點27,500水平點。本來千餘點的波幅沒有甚麼大不了，若然只是小注買正股博反彈，問題應該不大。筆者在「午間教路」所建議的中銀香港(02388)及友邦保險(01299)，就更加沒有問題。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其事件的影響，暫時仍未到爆煲階段，但周二港股跌得較外圍厲害。就算日股已大幅反彈，A股回穩，歐美股市期貨已回升，恒指下午跌幅卻一度擴大至414點，似是期指大戶刻意殺倉。<br />\n<br />\n跌市元兇是舜宇光學(02382)，因其公布業績後，似乎基金即時要洗倉，高峰期跌逾三成，以恒指成分股來說，跌勢實在罕見。雖然其業績表現令投資者失望，但如此這般的下跌，歸根究柢只有一個原因，就是「貴」！<br />\n<br />\n基本分析始終是長線投資者的依據，價格是否合理，估值是否極昂貴，都是投資決策的重點。股價「炒」得勁，「炒」得高，不代表此股值得買、值得長揸。打着「科技」、「新經濟」的牌頭，說到天上有地下無，最終還不是大戶誇大其價值，引散戶入場的炒作伎倆？<br />\n<br />\n觀乎去年的新經濟股，包括股王騰訊(00700)、手機孖寶、眾安在綫(06060)、閱文(00772)、易鑫(02858)等，從高位計，跌幅逾三至七成，風險程度基本上跟很多細價股無異。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180815/bkn-20180815001510625-0815_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180815%2Fbkn-20180815001510625-0815_00842_001.html&d=ypmzyxijdUPvV7XhVUVVfMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=26f29e52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180815/bkn-20180815001510625-0815_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"aa7689db27557443f25892c7cfa64704fb2a2a28","tid":779840,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:39:59.000Z","msg":"All IT stock need die<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270bc998ebe3b87e33bf1271fbae6dcfe2a2c22f","tid":779840,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:43:00.000Z","msg":"師傅好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fe231935c52eb72c464e1f0fdca26a8fb30ae0","tid":779840,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"長和夠平啦，又咪跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde8f433d3e27c32a7a5af722afeb36b5a52480a","tid":779840,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:46:06.000Z","msg":"why no sleep<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf2ef7d442cc58a4c95d7d17e899c548cc6a586","tid":779840,"uid":52010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"老魔瘋狂追擊科技股<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14c4fa0714135dd9ba46896e1072b868bbe66a3","tid":779840,"uid":57862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T18:57:26.000Z","msg":"大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4e524ead22752e5cd9a50104a2b2f30d53f069","tid":779840,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T19:25:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccac5715544abe6fbc51c07a5510e058e41f7afa","tid":779840,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T22:47:18.000Z","msg":"又係U<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}